# Security, RBAC & Audit

## هر Endpoint جدید (Staff)

```typescript
@RequireAuth()
@RequireModule('installments')           // if module-scoped
@RequirePermission('installments.sale.create')
@ApplyDataScope()                        // all | branch | own
```

**Active branch (staff):** `X-Branch-Id` header or Redis session — must pass `canAccessBranch()` (ADR-015).  
JWT carries `tenantId` only — not `branchId`.

`{module}.{resource}.{action}` — e.g. `installments.payment.confirm`  
❌ vague `manage` alone

## Override precedence

```
DENY (user) > GRANT (user) > Role permissions > default DENY
```

User override = exception only — not full permission copy

## Actors (جدا — IDOR risk)

| Actor | Claim |
|-------|-------|
| Staff | `actor: staff`, `tenant_id` |
| Customer | `actor: customer` |
| Platform | `actor: platform` |

- Separate cookies: `hivork_staff` / `hivork_customer`
- Customer endpoints: only own data (`global_customer_id` from token)

## Audit اجباری

`sale.create|cancel` · `installment.waive` · `payment.confirm|reject` · `staff.*` · `role.*` · `settings.change` · `customer.import`

```typescript
AuditLog { actor, action, entity, old_value, new_value, tenant_id, ip }
// Immutable — no update/delete
```

## Auth

- Phone OTP — normalize `09xxxxxxxxx`
- Access 15min · Refresh httpOnly 30d
- Rate limit OTP: 3/min per phone

## Logging

- Structured (Pino) — `{ tenantId, event, entityId }`
- ❌ PII in log messages (phone, name in plain text)

